{"tid":2272345,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"被炒員工呼冤：高層指示去貨","createTime":"2020-11-05T04:16:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-05T04:21:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7e8823d939e5fc459f121494584be692f3ef96eb","tid":2272345,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T04:16:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201105/PZV4NS5XV5BVVBAP2HXKOMMA4M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201105%2FPZV4NS5XV5BVVBAP2HXKOMMA4M%2F&d=GnUrxgUttZjT4wJVsekm4PCGrV5sAEOTHy2vWGvapoA%3D&h=51b9bf3f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201105%2FPZV4NS5XV5BVVBAP2HXKOMMA4M%2F&h=a9b0e162\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201105/PZV4NS5XV5BVVBAP2HXKOMMA4M/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n被炒員工呼冤：高層指示去貨<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/BwYIyfWwj9Qu28BubBlwUNw031Q=/720x539/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EGAM2KK6LNH6DNI4Z7U7JLJAK4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FBwYIyfWwj9Qu28BubBlwUNw031Q%3D%2F720x539%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEGAM2KK6LNH6DNI4Z7U7JLJAK4.jpg&h=b783fa29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■陳小姐（圓圖）展示WhatsApp群組短訊，上級稱會帶備雅培疫苗以應付「麻煩客」。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】今次打錯針事件的負責機構香港傳染病預防動力，歸咎員工疏忽，指已即時開除；惟被炒女員工聲稱按上級指示做，不滿被迫「食死貓」，更出示WhatsApp群組對話，指高層曾要求下屬盡快用完備受爭議的賽諾菲疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：幼園70童打「致命」流感針  家長睹包裝盒揭發 轟機構違諾<br />\n<br />\n被炒員工陳小姐向本報聲稱，為學童注射疫苗當日，無收到上級要改用雅培疫苗的指示，發現打錯針後，上司接見她，指她沒看清楚更新文件而出錯。陳聲言文件寫用賽諾菲疫苗，惟上司駁斥有疑問應提出，她無提出屬疏忽，即時開除。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nWhatsApp紀錄：唔好比人知<br />\n<br />\n她向記者展示WhatsApp短訊稱高層曾指令下屬優先使用賽諾菲疫苗，姓李男上司留言：「法國的疫苗有信心的問題，我哋這幾天會盡量先出晒所有 VaxigripTetra（賽諾菲疫苗）。 」上司又教路若有 「議員想打、麻煩客想打」才提供雅培疫苗，更叮囑「千祈唔好比其他市民發現你這個舉動，唔係幾百人都話要嗰隻就真係冇」。<br />\n<br />\n香港傳染病預防動力的負責人李先生解釋，。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"1daa79ea55c1b33268f43f954425262921993142","tid":2272345,"uid":63779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T04:18:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c6a4177829d7ec0037cd04fbe89238aa9bd09c9","tid":2272345,"uid":66049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T04:19:58.000Z","msg":"嘩屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"087209cd51b64e686f26d92f98b196e0bd23a2e6","tid":2272345,"uid":24961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T04:20:55.000Z","msg":"仆街到"},{"pid":"57f72b568d823dc21d5064c9e774810f6313bcb3","tid":2272345,"uid":207247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T04:21:39.000Z","msg":"仆街到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}